---
description: Documentation and release notes rules
globs:
  - "README.md"
  - "docs/**/*.md"
alwaysApply: false
---

Prefer:
- docs aligned with actual code and supported PHP/Symfony ranges
- updating `CHANGELOG.md` and `docs/UPGRADING.md` for user-facing changes
- English for `docs/` and README

Do not invent commands or features not present in the repository.
